---
// Anti-Scam Component - Tailwind only, no custom CSS
---

<section class="py-12 bg-red-50 border-y-4 border-red-600">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
      <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-red-600 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"></path>
      </svg>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-red-900 mb-3">Beware of Locksmith Scams</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-red-600 font-bold">✗</span>
            <span>Fake low prices like - to get you on the phone</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-red-600 font-bold">✗</span>
            <span>Unlicensed technicians with no background checks</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-red-600 font-bold">✗</span>
            <span>Damaging locks to justify inflated charges</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-red-600 font-bold">✗</span>
            <span>Bait-and-switch tactics when they arrive</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="bg-green-100 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-lg p-4">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="font-bold text-green-900">Licensed & Verified</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-green-800 text-sm">CA License LCO 6687 • Background Checked • 15+ Years in Business • Honest Pricing</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
